with a goddamn pen?

742
00:52:37,006 --> 00:52:39,844
Well, you better hurry up.

743
00:52:40,006 --> 00:52:41,645
I'm coming to get you.

744
00:52:41,806 --> 00:52:43,564
I'm coming to get you,
Bishop.

745
00:52:43,726 --> 00:52:45,566
You're a dead man!

746
