It disgusts me.

760
00:54:02,767 --> 00:54:05,605
They don't deserve to live.

761
00:54:05,765 --> 00:54:09,404
I need to finish
our mission, Gavin,

762
00:54:09,565 --> 00:54:12,404
and you're not gonna stop me.

763
00:54:19,367 --> 00:54:21,924
Ludlow.

764
00:54:23,924 --> 00:54:26,644
